Class ProductContainerTreeNode

java.lang.Object

      gui.inventory.ProductContainerTreeNode
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, javax.swing.tree.MutableTreeNode, javax.swing.tree.TreeNode
public class ProductContainerTreeNode
extends javax.swing.tree.DefaultMutableTreeNode

ProductContainerTreeNode is a subclass of Swing's DefaultMutableTreeNode class that is used to represent nodes in the product container tree.
